title: Jenna Dewan posts a busty vacation selfie | Daily Mail Online
text: Share Jenna took to Instagram to share photos of the family vacation with her 3.7million followers. In one photo on the temporary Stories feed, the Supergirl actress throws up a peace sign and puckers up, wearing a bandeau bikini top with a white off-the-shoulder blouse as a cover-up. Open book: Jenna took to Instagram to share photos of the family vacation with her 3.7million followers Skinny mini: The actress put her lithe body on display in a photo - likely taken by her hunky beau, whose shadow can be seen in the shot - as she posed on a towel, facing the ocean The bikini top featured a floral design with three stringy red straps on the back and a matching strappy red bikini bikini bottom. The actress put her lithe body on display in a photo - likely taken by her hunky beau, whose shadow can be seen in the shot - as she posed on a towel, facing the ocean. In a later video, Jenna can be seen frantically rowing on a kayak, her hair whipping across her face. Independent woman! In a later video, Jenna can be seen frantically rowing on a kayak, her hair whipping across her face, as Channing records a video Time to rest: The danseuse takes a well-deserved break from rafting and lounges back on her pint-sized boat The caption read humorously: 'This is what learning to kayak in the rain, with upstream current and my partner filming instead of rowing looks like haha.' In the next shot, the danseuse takes a well-deserved break from rafting and lounges back on her pint-sized boat. The sportswear ambassador shared a photo of her handsome hubby funnily posing behind a 'your-face-here' cutout of a mermaid, which she later deleted. Post-and-delete: Jenna posted a photo of Tatum funnily posing behind a 'your-face-here' cutout of a mermaid The caption read: 'Coming soon to a theatre near you #splash.' One of Jenna's Instagram posts revealed two commenters who had seen the family the day of the photo. One user wrote: 'Met you and your family at the ice cream shop today, so down to earth, sweet, and beautiful! Enjoy your vacay!' Another commented: 'I had no idea that was you guys at the beach! Took me a minute. But my daughter enjoyed playing with your daughter! Very nice to meet you all.' Hiding from the sun: Jenna posted a sunny selfie on Valentine's Day The couple's vacation is well-deserved, as for the past year they have both been hard at work in their respective careers. Tatum just wrapped shooting for Kingsman: The Golden Circle and can next be seen in Steven Soderbergh's Logan Lucky, hitting theaters August 18. Meanwhile, Jenna will host Jennifer Lopez's upcoming NBC dance show World of Dance, as she gears up to create a still-untitled dance show for NBC with Channing, which landed a six-episode order.
